Hey, Kohei.

76
00:04:20,802 --> 00:04:22,471
You're a pretty boy.

77
00:04:22,637 --> 00:04:23,638
What?!

78
00:04:23,805 --> 00:04:29,019
If you enter, you'd probably win.
Use your charm to help our club.

79
00:04:29,186 --> 00:04:30,437
I'm sorry, but...

80
00:04:30,812 --> 00:04:33,982
