-Why not?

81
00:04:34,149 --> 00:04:36,193
You have Kohei.

82
00:04:36,443 --> 00:04:38,028
Hey, Iori.

83
00:04:38,195 --> 00:04:39,446
What?

84
00:04:40,363 --> 00:04:42,824
