320
00:17:19,121 --> 00:17:21,540
I'll have to give everyone this...

321
00:17:23,584 --> 00:17:25,628
-Here's some oolong tea!
-Here!

322
00:17:25,795 --> 00:17:28,297
-I still have some. I'm fine.
-Me too.

323
00:17:29,715 --> 00:17:30,800
There's more!

324
00:17:34,136 --> 00:17:35,763
Shaved ice is perfect for the sea!

325
00:17:35,930 --> 00:17:37,431
It has special syrup!

326
00:17:37,598 --> 00:17:39,100
I'm full.

327
00:17:39,267 --> 00:17:40,935
You guys can have it.

328
00:17:43,312 --> 00:17:45,564
What are you guys doing?

329
00:17:45,856 --> 00:17:47,900
Can I ask you something?

330
00:17:48,234 --> 00:17:50,403
Why are you trying to get Chii-chan drunk?

331
00:17:50,987 --> 00:17:52,530
What you're talking about!?

332
00:17:52,697 --> 00:17:54,824
That's a pretty extreme accusation!

333
00:17:54,991 --> 00:17:58,953
If you're trying to get her drunk, then I have an idea.

334
00:17:59,120 --> 00:18:00,788
No! That's not what we're doing!

335
00:18:00,955 --> 00:18:03,082
Then what were you trying to do?

336
00:18:03,249 --> 00:18:05,710
It can't be helped!

337
00:18:05,876 --> 00:18:07,712
No more tricks! Chisa!

338
00:18:08,713 --> 00:18:09,714
What?

339
00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:12,133
-Enter the women's beauty pageant!
-No.

340
00:18:12,550 --> 00:18:14,760
He'll kneel down naked and beg you! Please!

341
00:18:14,927 --> 00:18:16,304
Want me to step on him?

342
00:18:16,470 --> 00:18:18,222
Just answer yes or no!

343
00:18:18,389 --> 00:18:20,182
-Please!
-We're begging you!

344
00:18:20,349 --> 00:18:21,976
I said no!

345
00:18:22,435 --> 00:18:25,688
That won't work. If you're going
to ask her for something,

346
00:18:25,855 --> 00:18:27,982
you should tell her your reason.

347
00:18:30,192 --> 00:18:31,360
You don't have a reason?

348
00:18:31,527 --> 00:18:32,820
Well...

349
00:18:32,987 --> 00:18:36,490
If Chisa enters, we can get the prize money.

350
00:18:36,657 --> 00:18:40,119
Then we don't have to enter
the male pageant.

351
00:18:41,662 --> 00:18:43,998
I see. Now I understand.

352
00:18:44,165 --> 00:18:45,374
What about it, Chii-chan?

353
00:18:46,292 --> 00:18:47,710
No way.

354
00:18:49,211 --> 00:18:50,713
I was expecting this...

355
00:18:50,880 --> 00:18:53,007
You shouldn't have asked in the first place.

356
00:18:53,466 --> 00:18:55,259
What? She said no?

357
00:18:55,635 --> 00:18:57,595
We didn't even have a chance.

358
00:18:57,762 --> 00:19:00,514
So, now we have to enter the male pageant...

359
00:19:00,681 --> 00:19:02,266
It can't be helped.

360
00:19:02,558 --> 00:19:05,603
Who entered the pageant when it was your turn?

361
00:19:05,770 --> 00:19:07,521
Azusa entered the women's pageant.

362
00:19:07,938 --> 00:19:09,440
She is pretty.

363
00:19:09,607 --> 00:19:12,526
-She lost in the preliminaries though.
-Huh? Why?

364
00:19:12,693 --> 00:19:15,905
She forgot her swimsuit and competed in her underwear,
so she was disqualified.

365
00:19:16,072 --> 00:19:17,907
That's amazing.

366
00:19:18,157 --> 00:19:19,742
She wasn't embarrassed?

367
00:19:19,909 --> 00:19:21,327
She's that type of girl.

368
00:19:21,494 --> 00:19:22,661
No, that can't...

369
00:19:23,037 --> 00:19:25,623
Well, you'll find out soon.

370
00:19:26,165 --> 00:19:28,542
Take it off!

371
00:19:28,834 --> 00:19:31,170
If you lose, you have to spread your legs!

372
00:19:34,298 --> 00:19:37,093
All right! I'm going to go join them.

373
00:19:37,385 --> 00:19:38,552
Go ahead.

374
00:19:38,719 --> 00:19:40,930
Azusa likes that kind of stuff.

375
00:19:41,180 --> 00:19:43,015
Let me join!

376
00:19:43,182 --> 00:19:45,226
Okay! Huh!?

377
00:19:45,893 --> 00:19:47,311
-Really?
-Yeah.

378
00:19:47,478 --> 00:19:49,855
It's naked rock paper scissors!
You'll strip?

379
00:19:50,022 --> 00:19:51,190
Are you okay with that?

380
00:19:51,399 --> 00:19:53,692
If you lose, you strip!
It's naked rock paper scissors!

381
00:19:53,943 --> 00:19:56,112
I'm not going to get totally naked though.

382
00:19:56,278 --> 00:19:58,197
I'm a young girl, you know.

383
00:19:58,364 --> 00:20:01,200
-Oh, yeah.
-You're right.

384
00:20:01,575 --> 00:20:02,702
That's why...

385
00:20:03,035 --> 00:20:04,412
I've stuck band-aids on.

386
00:20:06,414 --> 00:20:07,623
I'll go first.

387
00:20:07,790 --> 00:20:09,208
But, Kitahara...

388
00:20:09,458 --> 00:20:11,127
You have nothing left to take off.

389
00:20:12,378 --> 00:20:14,255
There's nothing to worry about, Kohei.

390
00:20:14,422 --> 00:20:15,423
Just once.

391
00:20:15,589 --> 00:20:18,426
I'm going to bet everything on just one chance.

392
00:20:19,427 --> 00:20:20,010
HAIRPIN

393
00:20:21,387 --> 00:20:24,223
Tokki! Bukki! This guy is great!

394
00:20:24,390 --> 00:20:25,891
I'm glad you like him.

395
00:20:26,058 --> 00:20:27,226
He's talented, right?

396
00:20:27,643 --> 00:20:29,353
Let's compete on speed!

397
00:20:29,520 --> 00:20:32,273
I'm going to take this one standing.
You stay back, Kohei.

398
00:20:32,440 --> 00:20:34,358
No, you stay back.

399
00:20:37,236 --> 00:20:39,071
That was fun!

400
00:20:39,572 --> 00:20:41,824
-They're nice, right?
-Yeah.

401
00:20:42,199 --> 00:20:44,326
What's nice about them?

402
00:20:44,994 --> 00:20:46,829
I like them, though.

403
00:20:48,831 --> 00:20:50,833
-Hey, Chii-chan.
-Yes?

404
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:53,252
Why don't you enter the women's beauty pageant?

405
00:20:54,336 --> 00:20:55,337
No.

406
00:20:55,504 --> 00:20:59,091
-It's part of the joy of being born a woman.
-What do you mean?

407
00:21:00,384 --> 00:21:01,969
You know...

408
00:21:02,136 --> 00:21:05,973
Those guys never doubted
that you'd win, right?

409
00:21:06,515 --> 00:21:10,227
It's because they think
you're the cutest one, Chii-chan.

410
00:21:11,395 --> 00:21:15,232
If Chisa enters, we can get the prize money.

411
00:21:17,985 --> 00:21:18,986
What do you think?

412
00:21:19,987 --> 00:21:21,447
-Well...
-Huh?

413
00:21:21,614 --> 00:21:24,909
It's not that I won't do it no matter what...

414
00:21:28,454 --> 00:21:33,501
I just don't like how
they're trying to embarrass only me.

415
00:21:35,669 --> 00:21:37,213
HEARTTHROB
LEMON SOUR

416
00:21:37,379 --> 00:21:39,965
-What?
-You're right.

417
00:21:40,132 --> 00:21:42,259
