418
00:21:42,760 --> 00:21:44,553
Then let's do this.

419
00:21:48,182 --> 00:21:49,934
Thanks to Iori and Kohei,

420
00:21:50,100 --> 00:21:52,561
Chisa decided to enter the women's beauty pageant.

421
00:21:53,437 --> 00:21:56,232
-Really?
-She changed her mind overnight?

422
00:21:56,440 --> 00:21:58,526
So, there's something we want to give you.

423
00:21:59,360 --> 00:22:01,028
Here. Take this.

424
00:22:02,696 --> 00:22:03,906
Why?!

425
00:22:04,156 --> 00:22:07,660
Chisa said she'd enter the women's beauty pageant
under one condition.

426
00:22:07,826 --> 00:22:09,828
You guys have to enter the male pageant.

427
00:22:09,995 --> 00:22:11,747
Then why did we even...

428
00:22:11,914 --> 00:22:13,415
It was all for nothing!

429
00:22:13,666 --> 00:22:17,670
-You wear the girl's uniform!
-You're the one entering the joke category!

430
00:22:18,295 --> 00:22:20,130
They look like they're having fun.

431
00:22:20,297 --> 00:22:21,924
I'm glad they're close.

432
00:22:22,299 --> 00:22:25,177
-Everything's okay now, right?
-Yes.

433
00:22:27,263 --> 00:22:29,848
Well, I feel a little better now.

434
00:22:32,393 --> 00:22:33,394
DEEP BLUE AL FINE
KAYA MIZUKI

435
00:22:33,602 --> 00:22:35,688
Here's your mic, Kitahara.

436
00:22:35,896 --> 00:22:39,942
Me, too...? All right, let's do this!

437
00:22:40,109 --> 00:22:43,445
-Yeah, sing your heart out.
-You guys seem to be having fun.

438
00:22:45,114 --> 00:22:51,120
A fairytale whispers
In a fake world

439
00:22:51,287 --> 00:22:57,042
Hiding in the complete darkness

440
00:22:57,209 --> 00:23:03,007
I reach for the forbidden fruit
In my last days

441
00:23:03,173 --> 00:23:09,305
Now I know the meaning of the song about hope

442
00:23:09,471 --> 00:23:14,560
A broken gear will never stop again

443
00:23:14,727 --> 00:23:22,151
Even if I were to lose everything
I'd still want you to know

444
00:23:22,318 --> 00:23:28,240
Trapped in the sky so far away
I'm praying with ripped off wings

445
00:23:28,449 --> 00:23:34,204
Because we span together
The vows of areppegio

446
00:23:34,371 --> 00:23:40,127
If life sparkles only to the beat
of the resonating stars

447
00:23:40,294 --> 00:23:43,130
I'll sacrifice everything

448
00:23:43,297 --> 00:23:47,676
Till death do us apart

449
00:23:47,885 --> 00:23:49,762
Cheers!

450
00:23:54,558 --> 00:23:57,186
We're very sorry!

451
00:24:02,316 --> 00:24:05,110
Izu Spring Festival! Yay!

452
00:24:05,277 --> 00:24:06,904
I'm Chisa Kotegawa
from Peek-a-Boo!

453
00:24:07,071 --> 00:24:09,073
Take this!

454
00:24:13,911 --> 00:24:14,912
A ghost!

455
00:24:15,079 --> 00:24:16,872
